%pyspark

from pyjake.sparkmodule import udf_hour, udf_month, udf_d2wth

whole = spark.read.parquet('hdfs:///nl/witlab/cas/whole_srs.parquet')
whole_r = whole.withColumn('hour', udf_hour('time'))\
               .withColumn('month', udf_month('date'))\
               .withColumn('weather', udf_d2wth('date'))
whole_r.show(1)

%pyspark

whole_sel = whole_r.select('date', 'time', 'hour', 'uvi', 'illum', 'weather')
spring = whole_sel.where('weather = 0')
summer = whole_sel.where('weather = 1')
fall = whole_sel.where('weather = 2')
winter = whole_sel.where('weather = 3')

%pyspark

cl = spark.read.parquet('hdfs:///dayday/clean_days.parquet')
monthly = whole_r.select('date', 'time', 'hour', 'month', 'illum', 'uvi')\
                 .join(cl, 'date')

%md

# Seasonal Hourly Grouped BoxPlot

paragraphs.title: spring, srs, hourly grouped
paragraphs.text:
%pyspark
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import seaborn as sns

fig1, ax1 = plt.subplots(figsize=(24, 9))
ax1.set_ylim([0, 170000])
sns.boxplot(ax=ax1, x='hour', y='illum', data=spring.toPandas())
